Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch def xception_predict_breed(img_path):
    prediction = xception_model.predict(extract_Xception(path_to_tensor(img_path)))
    predicted_index = np.argmax(prediction)
    predicted_dog = dog_names[predicted_index]
    return predicted_dog

def xception_dog_breed_detector(img_path):
    if xception_dog_detector(img_path):
        print("Hello doggie!")
        predicted_breed = xception_predict_breed(img_path)
        print("You look like a {}".format(predicted_breed))
    elif face_detector(img_path):
        print("Hello human!")
        predicted_breed = xception_predict_breed(img_path)
        print("You look like a {}".format(predicted_breed))
    else:
        print("Unidentified thing!")

    plot_image(img_path)

I tested both the Xception and ResNet model for the 6 test images. I had 2 human faces, 2 dogs and 2 other images. The Xception model performed better. The Xception model identified both the humans, one of the dogs. The dog that it identified, it predicted the correct breed. Points of improvement:

  • Dog image that it did not recognize had a tilted head. That could possibly mean that the model needs more training on augmented images.
  • Since the new dataset used for transfer learning is smaller than the original dataset, the model could be overfitting. So increasing the new dataset size could improve it's performance.
  • Increasing the epoch may improve the performance.
